comment10.text=\r\n\ Return\ the\ most\ helpful\ comment.\ The\ most\ useful\ comment\ is\ the\r\n\ one\ with\ the\ highest\ vote\ balance.\ If\ there\ are\ multiple\r\n\ comments\ with\ equal\ highest\ balance,\ return\ any\ one\ of\ them.\r\n
